text:
Wow! The weather is amazing~!
Hey, Producer! Take a picture of Hinana!

Got it.
Just press here, right? Okay, here we go...
How is it? Did you take a good picture?

Yeah~!
Hinana looks super cute in it~

When we passed by here in the car the other day,
the sea was pitch black and we couldn't see anything.

Hey, Producer. Let's take some pictures
over there this time! By the shoreline!

Ah, of course.
Let's take lots of great photos.
